<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.7.1">
<l>āṉirai mēykkanī pōti yarumarun tāva taṟiyāy</l>
<l>kāṉaka mellām tirintuṉ kariya tirumēṉi vāṭa</l>
<l>pāṉaiyil pālaip parukip paṟṟātā rellām cirippa</l>
<l>tēṉi liṉiya pirāṉē ceṇpakap pūccūṭṭa vārāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lord, sweet like honey,</l>
<l rend="indent">going to graze the cowherd, wandering the whole forest</l>
<l rend="indent">so that your dark, holy body fades,</l>
<l rend="indent">and drinking milk [straight] from pots,</l>
<l rend="indent">while all [your] foes laugh,</l>
<l>you do not know that [you] are [our] rare medicine.</l>
<l>Come so that [I can] adorn [you] with Ceṇpaka blossoms!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
